title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Tackle The Black Box File from GTA Online: Agents of Sabotage for a Priority File Bonus
content:
Jodi has set her sights on the recording device aboard a hijacked jet in The Black Box File. Successfully complete the multi-stage operation — this week’s Priority File from the new Agents of Sabotage update — for an increased GTA$ payout.

On top of the premium payout, Priority File status means The Black Box File can only be completed one time this week. Once you’ve taken ownership of the Garment Factory, look for the Priority File tag when using the Darnell Inc. App.
